name: The King's Dreams: A Vibrational Throne
description:
The colours of the Chakra system run through his core.
He astrally moves beyond time and space.
A wizard of the age.
His spectrum is pure light and there is no part of the cosmos he cannot touch.
The Light.
The Presence.
This surely is Heavens glare?
He has the prism of colour between the eyes.
